# ============================================
# content-factory 开源边界(2026/7/5 准备开源)
# 决策:
#   1 = src/ templates/ bin/ scripts(已整合)/ docs/ examples/ tests/
#       topics-pool.md / SOP.md / README.md / CHANGELOG / CONTRIBUTING /
#       SECURITY / LICENSE / AGENTS / CLAUDE / SOURCE_OF_TRUTH
#       → 全部开源
#
#   2 = drafts/ publish/ tracking/ logs/ reports/ archives/
#       00-07 dbs 旧系统 / serenity-skill
#       → 本地保留,只从 .git 忽略(不物理删)
#
#   3 = 公告原文 PDF(每篇 100KB-5MB,可能数百篇)
#       → drafts/raw/*/cninfo/pdfs/ 忽略
#       → JSON 元数据 commit
# ============================================

# ── Private data(本地保留)──
drafts/posts/
drafts/candidates/
drafts/outlines/
drafts/raw/
drafts/research/
publish/
tracking/
logs/
reports/
archives/
serenity-skill/

# ── Legacy dbs-content-system 7 目录(早期试错,2026/6/29 已 ignore)──
00-规则与索引/
01-原始素材区/
02-内容单元库/
03-处理状态/
04-模板/
05-主题地图/
06-选题装配/
07-脚本与工具/

# ── PDF 大文件(只忽略 PDF,JSON 元数据 commit)──
**/cninfo/pdfs/*.PDF
**/cninfo/pdfs/*.pdf

